      "rationale": "FDA generic pump experiments conducted at 2.5 L/min/3000 RPM, 5 L/min/3000 RPM, 2.5 L/min/4500 RPM, 5 L/min/4500 RPM, and 3.75 L/min/3750 RPM. Flow and speed tolerances confirmed within ±3%. Temperature maintained at 37°C ± 0.5°C."
