      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) within 25% of experimental measurements across all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted NIH values compared against FDA experimental data across all five operating points. Maximum deviation was 18.4% at the 2.5 L/min/4500 RPM condition. Mean absolute error 11.2%. Level 2 output comparison achieved."
    },
